@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="lead">
        At AgriEnergy Connects, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>
        We may collect personal details such as your name, email address, phone number, and location to provide and improve our services.
    </p>

    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <p>
        Your data is used to personalize your experience, enhance our platform, and communicate with you regarding updates and support.
    </p>

    <h4>3. Data Protection</h4>
    <p>
        We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure your personal data is secure and protected from unauthorized access.
    </p>

    <h4>4. Sharing of Information</h4>
    <p>
        We do not share your personal information with third parties unless required by law or to provide essential services you’ve requested.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>
        You have the right to access, update, or delete your information at any time. Contact us if you have any questions regarding your data.
    </p>

    <h4>6. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
    </p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-4">
        Last updated: May 13, 2025
    </p>
</div>
